To increase statistical power, we treated individual peptides as observations of a given protein. Data were imported into the R statistical programming environment for subsequent analyses. Using the lme4 package64, a linear mixed effects model was applied to each protein with the following form:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
